---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Evans Performance" description="Evans Performance LTD Lead Generation Privacy Policy">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="border-b border-border">
      <div class="container px-4 py-6">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/><path d="M19 12H5"/></svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="container px-4 py-12 md:py-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Lead Generation Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-primary font-semibold mb-2">Evans Performance LTD</p>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-10">Last Updated: October 10, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-8">
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          This policy applies to information collected when you engage with our services, including when you submit your information through our LinkedIn lead generation forms, website, or advertisements. If you become a client, a separate Client Services Agreement will govern how we handle your health and performance data.
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">1. What Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">When you submit our LinkedIn lead form, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>LinkedIn profile URL</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">
            We may also collect information about how you interact with our website and advertisements through cookies and tracking technologies (see Section 8 for details).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">We use your contact information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>Contact you via email, phone calls (which may use automated dialing technology), and SMS text messages about our executive health optimization services</li>
            <li>Send marketing communications about our programs, resources, and offerings</li>
            <li>Schedule consultations if you express interest in our services</li>
            <li>Provide customer service and respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li>Improve our services and advertising performance by understanding how prospects engage with our business</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-6 p-6 bg-card rounded-xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4">SMS Text Message Consent</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              By submitting your information and checking the consent box, you expressly consent to receive automated marketing text messages (e.g., promotions, appointment reminders, and service updates) from Evans Performance at the phone number you provide.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Consent is not required as a condition of purchasing any goods or services.</li>
              <li>Message frequency varies based on your engagement and our marketing activities.</li>
              <li>Message and data rates may apply. Check with your mobile carrier for details.</li>
              <li>Text STOP to opt out at any time. Text HELP for assistance.</li>
              <li>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">
              By consenting, you acknowledge that you are authorized to provide this phone number and that you are the account holder or have the account holder's permission to receive texts at this number.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 p-6 bg-card rounded-xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Client SMS Communications</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              If you become a client of Evans Performance LTD, you will receive automated text messages as part of your coaching program. By signing your coaching agreement (via DocuSign), you consent to receive:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Weekly health check-in reminders with links to submit your progress</li>
              <li>90-day scorecard notifications with links to review your results</li>
              <li>Program-related updates and reminders</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">
              Message frequency varies based on your coaching program. Message and data rates may apply.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">
              <strong class="text-foreground">To opt out:</strong> Reply STOP to any message.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">
              <strong class="text-foreground">For help:</strong> Reply HELP or contact <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">
              Consent is not required as a condition of purchasing coaching services.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">3. Who Has Access to Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who help us deliver our services, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>Customer relationship management (CRM) platforms</li>
            <li>Email marketing and communication tools</li>
            <li>Appointment scheduling services</li>
            <li>Analytics and advertising platforms (including Google and LinkedIn)</li>
            <li>SMS/text messaging services</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 p-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg border border-primary/20">
            <strong class="text-primary">Important:</strong> No mobile information will be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing/promotional purposes. All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4">
            These service providers are contractually required to protect your information and use it only to provide services to us. Some platforms (Google, LinkedIn) may use de-identified, aggregated data for their own analytics purposes as described in their privacy policies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">4. How Long We Keep Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            We retain your contact information for up to 7 years for business record-keeping, marketing, and legal compliance purposes, unless you request deletion or opt out of communications.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            If you request deletion of your information, we will delete it within 30 days, except where retention is required by law (e.g., tax records, fraud prevention, or pending legal matters).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Unsubscribe from Emails</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Every marketing email includes an unsubscribe link. Click it to stop receiving marketing emails.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Opt Out of SMS Messages</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Reply "STOP" to any text message to opt out of SMS communications.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Opt Out of Phone Calls</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">To stop receiving marketing calls, email <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a> or inform us during any call. We will honor your request within 30 days.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Request Deletion</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">To request deletion of your information from our systems, email us at <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a> with "Delete My Information" in the subject line. We'll process deletion requests within 30 days, though we may retain certain records for legal compliance purposes.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Access Your Information</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">You can request a copy of the information we have about you by emailing <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no internet transmission is completely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security of transmitted information.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">7. Geographic Scope</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Our services are currently marketed to individuals in the United States. By submitting your information, you consent to the processing and storage of your data in the United States.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">8. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">We use cookies and tracking technologies (including LinkedIn Insight Tag and Google Analytics) on our website to track visitor behavior and optimize our advertising. This may place cookies on your device. You can control cookies through your browser settings. Learn more about how these platforms use data in their respective privacy policies.</p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">We may also retarget you with advertising on LinkedIn, Google, and other platforms based on your interaction with our lead forms and website. You can opt out of interest-based advertising at <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">www.aboutads.info/choices</a> or <a href="https://www.networkadvertising.org/choices" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">www.networkadvertising.org/choices</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">9. California Privacy Rights (CCPA/CPRA)</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">If you are a California resident, you have specific rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) and California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA):</p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Right to Know</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">You have the right to request disclosure of the personal information we collect, use, disclose, and sell about you. This includes the categories of information, sources, business purposes, and third parties with whom we share data.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Right to Delete</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">You have the right to request deletion of your personal information, subject to certain exceptions (e.g., legal obligations, fraud prevention, or completing transactions).</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Right to Opt-Out of Sharing</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">We may "share" your information with third parties (Google, LinkedIn) for advertising purposes, which may be considered a "sale" under CCPA. You have the right to opt out of this sharing. To opt out, email us at <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a> with "Do Not Share My Information" in the subject line.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Right to Non-Discrimination</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">You have the right to not receive discriminatory treatment for exercising your CCPA rights.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Exercising Your Rights</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a>. We will respond to verifiable requests within 45 days. We may require verification of your identity before processing requests.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">10. Minors</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Our services are intended for individuals 18 years of age or older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors under 18. If we become aware that we have collected information from a minor, we will promptly delete it. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a minor, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">11. Updates to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. The "Last Updated" date at the top of this page indicates when changes were last made. Your continued engagement with our lead forms after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">12. Questions or Concerns</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">If you have questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your information, contact us at:</p>
          <address class="not-italic text-muted-foreground p-4 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border">
            <strong class="text-foreground">Evans Performance LTD</strong><br />
            1500 N GRANT ST #6423<br />
            DENVER, CO, 80203, USA<br />
            <a href="mailto:support@evansperformancesystems.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@evansperformancesystems.com</a>
          </address>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="border-t border-border py-8">
      <div class="container px-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Evans Performance LTD. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
